            "text": "$(li)$(bold)$(l:the_world/flora#standard_plants)Standard Plant Types$()$(li)$(bold)$(l:the_world/flora#aquatic_plants)Aquatic Plant Types$()$(li)$(bold)$(l:the_world/flora#medicinal_plants)Medicinal Plants$()$(li)$(bold)$(l:the_world/flora#spices)Spices$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#basil)Basil$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#bay)Bay Laural$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#cardamom)Cardamom$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#cilantro)Cilantro$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#cumin)Cumin$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#oregano)Oregano$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#pimento)Pimento$()$(li2)$(l:the_world/flora#vanilla)Vanilla$()$(li)$(bold)$(l:the_world/flora#seed_ball)Seed Ball$()"
        },
        {
            "anchor": "intro",
			"type": "patchouli:spotlight",
            "title": "Intro to Earth Flora",
            "item": {
                "tag": "tfc:plants"
            },
            "text": "Earth is an incredibly diverse planet when it comes to flora. Unlike in vanilla $(thing)Minecraft$()--Plants in $(bold)$(#ff0fb7)TerraFirma$()$()$(bold)$(#595959)Greg$()$() spawn based on local $(l:the_world/climate#climate)Climate Conditions$()."
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "Plants may be difficult to find during some $(l:the_world/climate#seasons)Seasons$() as they go through cycles of flowering and laying dormant, or changing color as the local temperature changes.$(br2)Colorful flowers can typically be crushed in a $(l:mechanics/quern)Quern$() for $(l:mechanics/dye)Dye$(). While some plants can be used for making $(l:the_world/flora#medicinal_plants)medicine$() or $(l:the_world/flora#spices)meals$()."
        },
